{"tid":2300143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分享幾年前 連/高登既聖誕卡","createTime":"2020-11-25T09:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T13:46:16.000Z","uid":35746,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8e54f58d2c4a898dc5926f29b5836786be3afe","tid":2300143,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"自己好鍾意儲低朋友既信 / 聖誕卡之類<br />\n<br />\n感覺好warm,雖然一早已經冇聯絡，但往後睇番都會 會心微笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHyRQMd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHyRQMd.jpg&h=4292c2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張係2013年 已經有7年歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oj0s8x5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foj0s8x5.jpg&h=35c0cf91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28TN8x9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28TN8x9.jpg&h=53e2b24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個係2014年 12月雨傘之後 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEhSAdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEhSAdt.jpg&h=b8ba2f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvcvmTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvcvmTy.jpg&h=b54d5320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依張好似16定17年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他巴打有冇類似既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54136d9bc16ebd80803b009b1b03f72086d107c0","tid":2300143,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4c79213cf43a422a34a01ea609743fbe90dccc","tid":2300143,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"寫過比人又收過人地寫，有初中，有DSE, 有大學生。其中有一個至宜家都有聯絡。"},{"pid":"d4b20a5a5ac1501bab09c182e71c45d037a1f635","tid":2300143